Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan wants second term
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xcbq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Feb 1984
President Reagan announces he will join the race for a second term in the White House. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less